o, mente y emociones/esp\u00edritu.\nLa MTC no observa la enfermedad como tal, sino que el diagnostico y tratamiento viene dado por una serie de s\u00edntomas y signos que provocan un patr\u00f3n de desarmon\u00eda.\nEl diagn\u00f3stico viene dado por informaci\u00f3n obtenida de los s\u00edntomas y signos as\u00ed como la observaci\u00f3n de la lengua y la palpaci\u00f3n del pulso. La forma de actuaci\u00f3n de la MTC es restablecer el equilibrio del organismo tratando este patr\u00f3n.", "language": null, "image": "https://centreholistic.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Centre-Holistic-logo-horizontal-couleurs.svg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#main", "https://centreholistic.com/aviso-legal/", "https://centreholistic.com/centre-holistic-barcelona/", "https://centreholistic.com/contacto/", "https://centreholistic.com/", "https://centreholistic.com/noticias/", "https://centreholistic.com/politica-de-cookies/", "https://centreholistic.com/politica-de-privacidad/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-adelgazar/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-adicciones/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-circulatorio/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-digestivo/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-fertilidad/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-trastornos-menstruales-ginecologia/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-pediatria/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-oftalmologia/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-piel/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/holistic-post-parto/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/holistic-preparto/", "https://centreholistic.com/programa-holistic/programa-holistic-respiratorio-y-defensas/", "https://centreholist